Trung Nguyen Legend's preparation is the same as anywhere else. Tasty. However, as for this location, this is the first place I visited to enjoy Trung Nguyen nearly 10 years ago. Because me and my friends are in District 10. I got married to GV, so every night when I go on dates with friends, I choose TN HVT in the middle, so this shop is so familiar. Until one of her friends hunted for something and occasionally got a discount code. Every time I use a discount code, it means the service is poor. Normally for glass cups and crockery cups, there is a discount code for portable plastic S size cups to take away even if customers are already seated at the table. While going to other TN Legend at the Airport or District 10, they are still served in glass or ceramic cups. I'm allergic to coffee made from plastic cups. It loses the delicious taste of coffee. Sometimes there are discount codes, but that kind of service is really "disrespecting customers". I think the restaurant should change this service style. Now my friends don't want to go to this restaurant anymore. Normally there is no discount code, so I happily order a portion of Rumi Cafe for 129k. Don't look down on customers holding discount codes. Discourage this point. It's lovely to have Mr. NV keep the car.

There's nothing here, once and for all, never to return.

Actually, I come to Trung Nguyen a lot because I feel satisfied with the space and the service of the staff. However, after yesterday, I decided not to visit Trung Nguyen anymore for several reasons: - The security guard was not enthusiastic about arranging a car for the customer. When he left to pick up the car, he only came to pick up the ticket while his eyes were still focused on the phone screen playing games. - Trung Nguyen HVT has just had a change in service staff and the feeling is that Trung Nguyen no longer really cares about staff training. When guests came in, there was no greeting even though my companion and I politely said "hello". When going to the 2nd floor, it was no exception, the staff did not greet guests at all. - When ordering, they didn't say anything, didn't confirm what the customer ordered, and didn't even say yes - Actually, the image of the employee making a drink while mouthing something is very offensive. The male waiter on the 2nd floor yesterday left me with a very bad impression about that. - Normally when I leave, I always receive thanks from the staff. I was even very impressed with the cashier girl on the first floor a while ago because of her friendliness. But nowadays, employees hardly know how to say thank you Maybe I'm picky myself, but if I work on service, I think it's better to have perfection to create a good impression on customers.

Delicious coffee but excellent service mixed with modern and classic. I like the old Trung Nguyen style better because after drinking and paying, it's easy for me to invite anyone while here you have to pay below and go up to serve and bring it up. Where is my old taste for coffee!!!???

Today when I entered the restaurant, the cleaning staff had not yet swept the restaurant. The customers who were sitting were still sweeping and mopping the floor, causing dangerous slippery conditions. Please check the general management of the restaurant.
There are many seats and the space is comfortable. The staff are very good and give dedicated advice
Good coffee and many options for different flavors. Need to serve additional types of tea for guests who come along but do not know how to drink coffee
At 8:00 p.m., I ordered a drink. 8:15 p.m. drinks available.  And at 8:25 a.m., the staff said the restaurant was closed. Before that, the restaurant staff didn't say anything. :(
Nice view restaurant Clean drinks Breakfast and pastries are available for sale The restaurant has a long wait, even though it's not very crowded.

Trung Nguyen Coffee is very delicious and has many types to choose from. This is one of the chain of Trung Nguyen Coffee shops. Due to family disputes of the leader, Trung Nguyen Coffee gradually lost its position in the market.
The layout of the 2-front corner shop is sketchy and the minimalist style does not show its strengths like other shop systems!

Visit the restaurant on the 28th of Tet. Cars have to be towed in and out by themselves, which is very difficult because there are so many cars stuck in traffic. When parking the car, giving the ticket, taking the ticket, then returning to the seat, it's very unfriendly, leaving the customer to deal with their own car.  Service is okay, not satisfied
